No floor space? No problem! ✨This total body workout challenges every part of your body...𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐣𝐮𝐬𝐭 𝐚 𝐬𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐥𝐞 𝐛𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐰𝐚𝐥𝐥! 🔥These moves are perfect for sneaking in a quick routine at home, in the office (which nowadays is still your home ), or even when you’re on the road (you know that hallway from your bedroom to your living room? Yep, that’s right!)⁣🤣
⁣
1. Wall squat clam x 20⁣
2. Sprint against the wall x 20s⁣
3. Single-leg bridge up x 10 each side⁣
4. Single-leg wall sit x 10 each side⁣
5. Single leg wall lunge x 10 each side⁣
6. Crunches x 20⁣
7. Bridge walk ups x 10 up & down⁣
8. Pikes x 5⁣
⁣
Repeat the circuit three times, and remember to watch till the end for some satisfying stretching! ⁣😌
⁣
𝐒𝐀𝐕𝐄 this workout for your next sweat sesh and 𝐓𝐀𝐆 your exercise buddy to try it at home!⁣💖
⁣
Bye, boring flat surface! 👋
Hi, new workout partner! ⁣😍
